A cyberpunk scene depicting a massive underground prison-like facility filled with endless rows of cramped workstations, where shadowy figures hunch over glowing screens in near darkness. Neon pipes and exposed wiring snake across industrial concrete walls. In the foreground, a single empty chair with broken chains suggests escape. The color palette is dominated by harsh fluorescent greens and deep shadows, with occasional bursts of warning-red emergency lights. Steam rises from floor grates, and holographic productivity metrics float ominously above each station. The perspective is from a high angle, emphasizing the scale and dehumanizing repetition of the space, creating a commentary on exploitative labor practices in the tech industry.
